21 May Acting Minister in the Presidency, Khumbudzo Ntshavheni, together with Deputy Minister in the Presidency, Thembi Siweya, will deliver the GCIS Budget Vote, today, highlighting the vision and strategic points for the Department of Government Communication and Information System for the year 2021/22. The GCIS Budget Vote virtual presentation will take place as follows:Date: Friday 21 May 2021Time: 10h00-12h15 Virtual links:Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/parliamentofRSA Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/parliamentofRSA YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/ParliamentofRSA Enquiries: Ms Phumla WilliamsCell: 083 501 0139